    http://people.apache.org/~ltheussl/maven-stage-site/developers/mojo-api-specification.html
    https://stackoverflow.com/questions/10697964/how-to-process-project-sources-in-maven-plugin
    http://maven.apache.org/developers/mojo-api-specification.html
    -->

</project>